A total of 156 more COVID-19 related deaths that occurred yesterday [11 Aug 2021] were confirmed by the Director-General of Health Services today [12 Aug 2021], pushing the death toll to 5620.

According to the Government Information Department, 69 females and 87 males are among the deceased.

